------------------------------------------------------------------
RACHEL'S AMAZING BEAUTIFUL HACKY PARALLEL COMMUNICATION EXPERIMENT
------------------------------------------------------------------

Current issues: The write and read commands can overlap depending on clock speed differences. Need more waiting.

The software currently uses 18 pins - pins 0-7 for send, pins 8-15 for receive, and pins 16 and 17 for signalling the other pi.

This depends on the pigpio libraries found at https://abyz.me.uk/rpi/pigpio/
